      "text": "'Accept your end peacefully, for that is the destination of all.'\n\nOn Sunset Isle, her longing had once taken form as a phantom—yet even that proved nothing more than a fleeting dream. Despite the weight of her regrets, Regina shut her eyes and surrendered to the fate that awaited her.\n\nBut then, radiant sunlight touched her skin once more.\n\nWhat realm is this? By whom was she called back from the void?\n\nPerhaps her story was never meant to end on that distant shore?",
